longBusinessSummary: National United Resources Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the trading of coking coal, fuel oil, and aluminum rods in China and Singapore. It operates through three segments: Resources Trading, Media and Advertising, and Online Platform. The company is also involved in the operation of outdoor advertisement mediums/billboards; design and production of advertisements; graphic and brand designing; provision of media management and consulting services; operating chain broadcasting advertising networks; and provision of advertising and information consultancy services. In addition, it operates an online trading platform and offers spot delivery services for precious metals, such as silver and copper, as well as transaction settlement management, commodity delivery management, and related consulting services. Further, the company provides investment consultancy and corporate planning services; asset and investment management services; logistics and transport services; and management services. Additionally, it processes and trades aluminum. The company was formerly known as China Outdoor Media Group Limited and changed its name to National United Resources Holdings Limited in January 2014. National United Resources Holdings Limited is based in Central, Hong Kong.
